Subject: drm/xe: Set default MOCS value for cs instructions
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: e3ec5e75911b04b5e9ce67907024d7c5d9a6cb99
